Source: blizzard-cpp-sdk
Version: 1.0.0
Upstream-URL: https://github.com/rdk-gdcs/BlizzardCppSdk.git
Upstream-Ref: main
Build-Depends: libprotobuf-dev, protobuf-compiler, grpc++, libgrpc++-dev, libspdlog-dev

Package: blizzard-cpp-sdk
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Blizzard C++ SDK library - runtime
 Blizzard C++ SDK is a library for building applications that communicate
 with the Blizzard platform. It provides transport mechanisms including
 gRPC and WebSocket support, along with protocol buffer integration for
 efficient data serialization.
 .
 This package contains the runtime libraries.

Package: libblizzard-cpp-sdk-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: blizzard-cpp-sdk (= ${version})
Description: Blizzard C++ SDK library - development files
 Blizzard C++ SDK is a library for building applications that communicate
 with the Blizzard platform.
 .
 This package contains the development headers, CMake configuration files,
 and static libraries needed to build applications using the Blizzard C++ SDK.
